 "I need a referral to a contractor in your network"], "required": true}, {"key": "trades_needed", "type": "multiselect", "q": "What type of work do you need?", "sub": "We’ll match you with trusted pros in our network.", "options": ["General contractor", "Kitchen / bath remodel", "Roofing", "Electrical", "Plumbing", "HVAC", "Flooring", "Windows & doors", "Landscaping", "Pool", "Addition / structural", "Other"], "showIf": {"key": "contractor_status", "in": ["I need a referral to a contractor in your network"]}, "required": true}, {"key": "reno_loan_before", "type": "choice", "q": "Have you done a renovation loan before?", "options": ["Yes", "This is my first time"], "required": true}, {"key": "credit_score", "type": "choice", "q": "What is your estimated credit score?", "options": ["780+", "740 - 779", "700 - 739", "660 - 699", "620 - 659", "580 - 619", "Below 580"], "required": true}, {"key": "military_service", "type": "choice", "q": "Are you or your spouse an active military member, reserve member or veteran?", "options": ["Active Service", "Veteran", "Non Active Reserve National Guard", "None"], "required": true}, {"key": "employment_status", "type": "choice", "q": "What’s your employment status?", "options": ["Employed", "Self Employed / 1099 Independent Contractor", "Retired"], "required": true}, {"key": "annual_income", "type": "text", "q": "What is the gross annual income of the borrower or borrowers?", "placeholder": "$", "inputmode": "numeric", "required": true}, {"key": "bankruptcy_7yr", "type": "choice", "q": "Have you filed for bankruptcy in the last 7 years?", "options": ["Yes", "No"], "required": true}, {"key": "foreclosure_7yr", "type": "choice", "q": "Have you filed for foreclosure in the last 7 years?", "options": ["Yes", "No"], "required": true}, {"key": "contact", "type": "contact", "q": "Almost done — how can we reach you with your options?", "required": true}];
